              "question": "<p>Study the set of numbers given below and answer the question that follows:<br />\r\n112 202 325 413 621<br />\r\nWhich of the following numbers will be obtained, if the middle digit of the greatest number is added to the middle digit of the smallest number after adding one to each of the numbers?</p>",
