                }
              ],
              "correctOptionId": 2,
              "explanation": "<p>After adding 1 to each of the given numbers, we have<br />\r\n113 203 326 414 622<br />\r\nMiddle digit of the greatest number (622) is 2 and middle digit of the smallest number (113) is 1.<br />\r\nSo, required sum = 2 + 1 = 3</p>"
